title: Jordan 4 Taupe Haze Bulk
body:
Please fill out the bulk order form If you would like to order and we will be in contact.
UK minimum order quantity = 3 pairs
EU minimum order quantity = 8 pairs
14-21 Day Delivery from the day you have paid
Please be aware this time frame is an estimation
Theres only minimal updates we can provide as to when your delivery will arrive
No tracking is provided until the stock arrives In the UK.
